  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the char-grilled onions and cook until caramelized, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the diced potatoes to the skillet and cook until they start to brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper to the skillet and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sugar snap peas to the skillet and cook until tender, about 3 minutes.",
    "Flatten the potatoes slightly with a spatula and continue cooking for another 2 minutes, until they're crispy and golden brown.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with a squeeze of lemon juice.",
